{"version":2,"source":"https:\/\/excalidraw.com","appState":{"shouldCacheIgnoreZoom":false,"exportScale":2,"defaultSidebarDockedPreference":false,"openMenu":null,"showWelcomeScreen":true,"currentItemStrokeColor":"#1e1e1e","bindMode":"orbit","exportWithDarkMode":false,"lockedMultiSelections":{},"currentItemRoughness":1,"currentItemTextAlign":"left","exportBackground":true,"scrolledOutside":false,"selectedElementIds":{},"zenModeEnabled":false,"currentItemStartArrowhead":null,"zoom":{"value":0.216059},"theme":"light","activeTool":{"locked":false,"fromSelection":false,"lastActiveTool":null,"type":"selection","customType":null},"exportEmbedScene":false,"gridStep":5,"lastPointerDownWith":"mouse","selectedGroupIds":{},"currentItemBackgroundColor":"transparent","scrollY":431.39278190871335,"penDetected":false,"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff","name":"Untitled-2026-03-04-1220","currentItemFontFamily":5,"currentItemArrowType":"round","currentItemOpacity":100,"preferredSelectionTool":{"type":"selection","initialized":true},"scrollX":980.63294883569802,"stats":{"open":false,"panels":3},"objectsSnapModeEnabled":false,"gridSize":20,"gridModeEnabled":false,"openSidebar":null,"currentItemRoundness":"round","currentItemStrokeStyle":"solid","editingGroupId":null,"previousSelectedElementIds":{},"currentChartType":"bar","currentItemStrokeWidth":2,"cursorButton":"up","currentItemEndArrowhead":"arrow","currentItemFillStyle":"solid","currentItemFontSize":20,"selectedLinearElement":null,"penMode":false},"files":{},"elements":[{"isDeleted":false,"seed":383484317,"roughness":1,"strokeWidth":2,"id":"brl49Bg3IXYrZXp00x0ur","strokeStyle":"solid","fontSize":36,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","text":"Ticket Booking System","updated":1772704277992,"locked":false,"version":29,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b9g","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Ticket Booking System","height":45,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2037132356,"textAlign":"left","lineHeight":1.25,"fontFamily":8,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"angle":0,"x":717,"y":241,"width":415.7999267578125},{"isDeleted":false,"seed":1275183379,"roughness":1,"strokeWidth":2,"id":"I7KuhUsCG1wg6mLcKBI4i","strokeStyle":"solid","fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","text":"1. Event & Venue Service\n2. Search Service\n3. Booking & Inventory Service","updated":1772704277992,"locked":false,"version":33,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b9h","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. Event & Venue Service\n2. Search Service\n3. Booking & Inventory Service","height":75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1139714556,"textAlign":"left","lineHeight":1.25,"fontFamily":8,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"angle":0,"x":559,"y":479,"width":330},{"isDeleted":false,"seed":1224304371,"roughness":1,"strokeWidth":2,"id":"KKMORwR-TD-6E4r2vnuYA","strokeStyle":"solid","fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","text":"1. Venue\n\nPOST \/api\/v1\/venues\n{name, address:{street, city,district,state,pin,…etc}, location:{lat,lon}, imageUrls}\n\n- Admins can create venues which are nothing but MovieTheater\/Auditorium etc.\n- The request lands on the API gateway and routed to the Events&Venues service.\n- Venues service will add this entry in the Venues table.\n  Venue (id, name, address, location:{lat,lon}, imageUrls:[s3Keys])\n- Images are stored in s3 and thier keys are stored in venue record.\n\n- Later an Hall\/Screen is created under this venue\n\nPOST \/api\/v1\/venues\/{venueId}\/hall\n{hallName,seatLayout}\n- Request lands on the Events&Venues service and creates an entry in the Hall table.\n  Hall (id, venueId, hallName, seatLayout)\n\nSeatLayout might look like this\n{\n    sections:[\n        {\n            id, name, …metadata,\n            rows:[\n                label,\n                seats:[\n                    {id, label, coordinates:{x,y},…metadata}\n                ],\n                …metadata\n            ]\n        }\n    ]\n}","updated":1772704277992,"locked":false,"version":989,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b9i","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. Venue\n\nPOST \/api\/v1\/venues\n{name, address:{street, city,district,state,pin,…etc}, location:{lat,lon}, imageUrls}\n\n- Admins can create venues which are nothing but MovieTheater\/Auditorium etc.\n- The request lands on the API gateway and routed to the Events&Venues service.\n- Venues service will add this entry in the Venues table.\n  Venue (id, name, address, location:{lat,lon}, imageUrls:[s3Keys])\n- Images are stored in s3 and thier keys are stored in venue record.\n\n- Later an Hall\/Screen is created under this venue\n\nPOST \/api\/v1\/venues\/{venueId}\/hall\n{hallName,seatLayout}\n- Request lands on the Events&Venues service and creates an entry in the Hall table.\n  Hall (id, venueId, hallName, seatLayout)\n\nSeatLayout might look like this\n{\n    sections:[\n        {\n            id, name, …metadata,\n            rows:[\n                label,\n                seats:[\n                    {id, label, coordinates:{x,y},…metadata}\n                ],\n                …metadata\n            ]\n        }\n    ]\n}","height":825,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":925238212,"textAlign":"left","lineHeight":1.25,"fontFamily":8,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"angle":0,"x":567,"y":755,"width":935},{"isDeleted":false,"seed":60302771,"roughness":1,"strokeWidth":2,"id":"lGxsv1tSk9PJCFsVb-6O_","strokeStyle":"solid","fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","text":"2. Event Creation\n\nPOST \/api\/v1\/events\n{eventName, imageUrl, ..metadata}\n\nPUT \/api\/v1\/events\/venues\n{venues:[{venueId,hallId,date,time}]}\n\n- Admins creates events and attach venues to it.\n- Requests gets lands on the Events&Venues Service.\n\n- Event record gets created and added in the events table.\n  Event {id, name, imageUrl, …metadata}\n\n- A record gets added in the EventVenues table.\n  EventVenues {eventId, venueId, hallId, date, time}\n  \n","updated":1772704277992,"locked":false,"version":508,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b9j","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"2. Event Creation\n\nPOST \/api\/v1\/events\n{eventName, imageUrl, ..metadata}\n\nPUT \/api\/v1\/events\/venues\n{venues:[{venueId,hallId,date,time}]}\n\n- Admins creates events and attach venues to it.\n- Requests gets lands on the Events&Venues Service.\n\n- Event record gets created and added in the events table.\n  Event {id, name, imageUrl, …metadata}\n\n- A record gets added in the EventVenues table.\n  EventVenues {eventId, venueId, hallId, date, time}\n  \n","height":450,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":956303996,"textAlign":"left","lineHeight":1.25,"fontFamily":8,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"angle":0,"x":571,"y":1708,"width":638},{"isDeleted":false,"seed":157792403,"roughness":1,"strokeWidth":2,"id":"TrIs65fjpZbliYjs4oJ3X","strokeStyle":"solid","fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","text":"3. ShowSeat creation\n\n- whenever an event show is created and event is published\n- Some worker (SeatManager\/ShowtimeInventory will consume this event and create seats for this show)\n- This worker will fetch hall latest layout and create show seats.\n  ShowSeat ( eventId, showId, venueId, hallId, secionId, rowId, seatId, price, category, coordinates,…metadata)\n- For a show all seats gets created.\n","updated":1772704277992,"locked":false,"version":452,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b9k","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"3. ShowSeat creation\n\n- whenever an event show is created and event is published\n- Some worker (SeatManager\/ShowtimeInventory will consume this event and create seats for this show)\n- This worker will fetch hall latest layout and create show seats.\n  ShowSeat ( eventId, showId, venueId, hallId, secionId, rowId, seatId, price, category, coordinates,…metadata)\n- For a show all seats gets created.\n","height":200,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1589177156,"textAlign":"left","lineHeight":1.25,"fontFamily":8,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"angle":0,"x":569.28402617955624,"y":2190.5031941998482,"width":1221},{"isDeleted":false,"seed":1241390333,"roughness":1,"strokeWidth":2,"id":"tUWdF3lHzs7eNc6AMPPhS","strokeStyle":"solid","fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","text":"4. View Events\n\n- Now admins has added events and created shows we can show this to the user.\n\n- Whenever user lands on the Home screen we can ask user to share location coordinates or city name\n  and we can fetch events\/shows nearby to the user.\n\n- this request lands on the Search Service.\n- Search service uses elastic search to find shows nearby user and returns back to the user.\n- whenever a show\/event is created that data is ingested into the elastic search indexes.\n\n- Users can also search events, venues, shows, etc.\n","updated":1772704277992,"locked":false,"version":614,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b9l","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"4. View Events\n\n- Now admins has added events and created shows we can show this to the user.\n\n- Whenever user lands on the Home screen we can ask user to share location coordinates or city name\n  and we can fetch events\/shows nearby to the user.\n\n- this request lands on the Search Service.\n- Search service uses elastic search to find shows nearby user and returns back to the user.\n- whenever a show\/event is created that data is ingested into the elastic search indexes.\n\n- Users can also search events, venues, shows, etc.\n","height":325,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":907107068,"textAlign":"left","lineHeight":1.25,"fontFamily":8,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"angle":0,"x":575.14068390696184,"y":2494.896347485711,"width":1089},{"isDeleted":false,"seed":1221878963,"roughness":1,"strokeWidth":2,"id":"GFgN8c_XLr-1ksrZVSKc9","strokeStyle":"solid","fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","text":"5. Select seats\n\n- User selected event, venue, show time\n- Now we will fetch seat layout with seat availability from backend for the specified showtime.\n- Seats are rendered using seat layout provided.\n- User selects seats and clicks proceed.\n- Now we will inform backend booking service to block this seat\n- We will create a record in the redis with 10min expiry for the seat with user id\n    - If user makes payment within this time we will allocate this seat otherwise we make seat available for other\n      users\n- We will return final amount and seat available status back to the user.\n- User clicks on proceed payment.\n- Request lands on the Booking service.\n- Service talks with payment gateway and return paymentIntent,clientSecret back to service \n  which are returned back to the client\n- Client devices mounts payment elements using this paymentIntent and clientSecret and makes the payment.\n- Once the payment is done payment gateway notifies booking service and booking service creates order.\n\n- Booking is confirmed to the client.","updated":1772704277992,"locked":false,"version":1198,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b9m","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"5. Select seats\n\n- User selected event, venue, show time\n- Now we will fetch seat layout with seat availability from backend for the specified showtime.\n- Seats are rendered using seat layout provided.\n- User selects seats and clicks proceed.\n- Now we will inform backend booking service to block this seat\n- We will create a record in the redis with 10min expiry for the seat with user id\n    - If user makes payment within this time we will allocate this seat otherwise we make seat available for other\n      users\n- We will return final amount and seat available status back to the user.\n- User clicks on proceed payment.\n- Request lands on the Booking service.\n- Service talks with payment gateway and return paymentIntent,clientSecret back to service \n  which are returned back to the client\n- Client devices mounts payment elements using this paymentIntent and clientSecret and makes the payment.\n- Once the payment is done payment gateway notifies booking service and booking service creates order.\n\n- Booking is confirmed to the client.","height":475,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1921180356,"textAlign":"left","lineHeight":1.25,"fontFamily":8,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"angle":0,"x":593.14068390696184,"y":2926.896347485711,"width":1254}],"type":"excalidraw"}